OL,5, An Indian court has ordered a zoo in   
OL,6, West Bengal state to change the names  
OL,7, of two lions after a hardline Hindu    
OL,8, group complained it hurt their         
OL,9, religious sentiments.                  
OL,11,FThe lioness was named after Hindu deity
OL,12,FSita while the lion was called Akbar,  
OL,13,Fafter the 16th Century Mughal ruler.   
OL,15,FVishwa Hindu Parishad (VHP) challenged 
OL,16,Fthis, saying that naming the lioness   
OL,17,Fafter a goddess was blasphemous.       
OL,19,FIt also objected to keeping the lions  
OL,20,Fin the same wildlife park.             
